      <body>
         <div>
            <head>Translated parts</head>
            <p xml:id="KR2g0003-start">
               <seg corresp="#KR2g0003_tls_006-18a.2" xml:lang="en" resp="CH" modified="2019-12-24T20:51:21.05+09:00">Master Yàn went on a mission to Chǔ, and since Master Yàn was a short man</seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2g0003_tls_006-18a.3" xml:lang="en" resp="CH" modified="2019-12-24T20:54:17.699+09:00">the Chǔ folks produced a Small Gate next to the Lesser Gate to welcome Master Yàn.</seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2g0003_tls_006-18a.4" xml:lang="en" resp="CH" modified="2019-12-24T20:54:28.195+09:00">Master Yàn did not enter through this Lesser Gate</seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2g0003_tls_006-18a.5" xml:lang="en" resp="CH" modified="2019-12-24T20:54:36.805+09:00">but said:</seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2g0003_tls_006-18a.6" xml:lang="en" resp="CH" modified="2019-12-24T20:55:17.204+09:00">"If I had been on a mission to Dog Country</seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2g0003_tls_006-18a.7" xml:lang="en" resp="CH" modified="2019-12-24T20:55:39.712+09:00">I would enter through the Dog Gate;</seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2g0003_tls_006-18a.8" xml:lang="en" resp="CH" modified="2019-12-24T20:56:13.492+09:00">But at this point I am on a mission to Chǔ</seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2g0003_tls_006-18a.9" xml:lang="en" resp="CH" modified="2019-12-24T20:57:57.309+09:00">and it is not appropriate for me to enter the capital through this Lesser Gate.</seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2g0003_tls_006-18a.10" xml:lang="en" resp="CH" modified="2019-12-24T20:59:05.237+09:00">The Butler in Chief adjusted the route to be taken and Master Yàn entered through the Main Gate</seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2g0003_tls_006-18a.11" xml:lang="en" resp="CH" modified="2019-12-24T20:59:20.741+09:00">to have his audience with the King of Chǔ.</seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2g0003_tls_006-18a.12" xml:lang="en" resp="CH" modified="2019-12-24T20:59:30.18+09:00">The King said:</seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2g0003_tls_006-18a.13" xml:lang="en" resp="CH" modified="2019-12-24T21:00:22.607+09:00">"Does Qǐ have no (decent) men?</seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2g0003_tls_006-18a.14" xml:lang="en" resp="CH" modified="2019-12-24T21:00:49.459+09:00">So that they send you, Sir, to go on a mission?</seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2g0003_tls_006-18a.15" xml:lang="en" resp="CH" modified="2019-12-24T21:01:58.44+09:00">"Línziī has three hundred wards.</seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2g0003_tls_006-18a.16" xml:lang="en" resp="CH" modified="2019-12-24T22:15:12.31+09:00">                                    When they spread their sleeves these form whole curtains,</seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2g0003_tls_006-18a.17" xml:lang="en" resp="CH" modified="2019-12-24T22:16:15.699+09:00">                                    and when they wipe off their sweat they create a whole rain of sweat.</seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2g0003_tls_006-18a.18" xml:lang="en" resp="CH" modified="2019-12-24T21:04:50.393+09:00">Shoulder to shoulder, and heel on heel they lead their lives.</seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2g0003_tls_006-18a.19" xml:lang="en" resp="CH" modified="2019-12-24T22:22:42.615+09:00">                                    Why should there be any lack people?"</seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2g0003_tls_006-18a.20" xml:lang="en" resp="CH" modified="2019-12-24T21:05:48.208+09:00">The King said:</seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2g0003_tls_006-18a.21" xml:lang="en" resp="CH" modified="2019-12-24T21:08:05.876+09:00">"Given that there are so many what did they send you for?"</seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2g0003_tls_006-18a.22" xml:lang="en" resp="CH" modified="2019-12-24T21:08:17.64+09:00">Master Yàn replied:</seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2g0003_tls_006-18a.23" xml:lang="en" resp="CH" modified="2019-12-24T21:08:55.367+09:00">"When Qǐ commissions missions</seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2g0003_tls_006-18a.24" xml:lang="en" resp="CH" modified="2019-12-24T21:09:30.003+09:00">these each have their own main purpose.</seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2g0003_tls_006-18a.25" xml:lang="en" resp="CH" modified="2019-12-24T21:10:01.937+09:00">The worthy ones they send on the missions to the worthy kings,</seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2g0003_tls_006-18a.26" xml:lang="en" resp="CH" modified="2019-12-24T21:11:26.824+09:00">and the useless ones they send on the missions to the useless kings.</seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2g0003_tls_006-18a.27" xml:lang="en" resp="CH" modified="2019-12-24T21:11:50.034+09:00">I am of the most useless kind</seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2g0003_tls_006-19a.1" xml:lang="en" resp="CH" modified="2019-12-24T21:28:06.157+09:00">so I've been sent straight on a mission to Chǔ. (Taiping Yulan reads 宜 "appropriately" for 直.</seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2g0003_tls_006-20a.1" xml:lang="en" resp="CH" modified="2019-12-25T00:27:42.786+09:00">Yànzǐ was going to Chǔ on an official mission.</seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2g0003_tls_006-20a.2" xml:lang="en" resp="CH" modified="2019-12-25T00:28:04.506+09:00">When the King of Chǔ heard about the visit</seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2g0003_tls_006-20a.3" xml:lang="en" resp="CH" modified="2019-12-25T00:28:18.162+09:00">he told his ministers:</seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2g0003_tls_006-20a.4" xml:lang="en" resp="CH" modified="2019-12-25T00:29:19.393+09:00">Yàn Yīng</seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2g0003_tls_006-20a.5" xml:lang="en" resp="CH" modified="2019-12-25T00:30:20.242+09:00">is the man with the greates expertise in eloquence.</seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2g0003_tls_006-20a.6" xml:lang="en" resp="CH" modified="2019-12-25T00:30:27.331+09:00">Now, when he comes here</seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2g0003_tls_006-20a.7" xml:lang="en" resp="CH" modified="2019-12-25T00:36:12.081+09:00">I would like to humiliate him.</seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2g0003_tls_006-20a.8" xml:lang="en" resp="CH" modified="2019-12-25T00:36:12.399+09:00">How can that be done?"</seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2g0003_tls_006-20a.9" xml:lang="en" resp="CH" modified="2019-12-25T00:36:12.671+09:00">A minister replied:</seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2g0003_tls_006-20a.10" xml:lang="en" resp="CH" modified="2019-12-25T00:36:12.88+09:00">"For the occasion of his coming here</seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2g0003_tls_006-20a.11" xml:lang="en" resp="CH" modified="2019-12-25T00:36:13.147+09:00">I beg to put some fellow in fetters</seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2g0003_tls_006-20a.12" xml:lang="en" resp="CH" modified="2019-12-25T00:36:13.389+09:00">pass by Your Majesty and go my way.</seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2g0003_tls_006-20a.13" xml:lang="en" resp="CH" modified="2019-12-25T00:36:13.551+09:00">Then Your Majesty must say:</seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2g0003_tls_006-20a.14" xml:lang="en" resp="CH" modified="2019-12-25T00:36:13.8+09:00">"Who's that?"</seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2g0003_tls_006-20a.15" xml:lang="en" resp="CH" modified="2019-12-25T00:36:14.068+09:00">And I will reply:</seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2g0003_tls_006-20a.16" xml:lang="en" resp="CH" modified="2019-12-25T00:36:14.584+09:00">"He is a man from Qí."</seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2g0003_tls_006-20a.18" xml:lang="en" resp="CH" modified="2019-12-25T00:39:52.074+09:00">                                    "What is he convicted of?"</seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2g0003_tls_006-20a.17" xml:lang="en" resp="CH" modified="2019-12-25T00:36:15.112+09:00">Then Your Majesty must say:</seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2g0003_tls_006-20a.27" xml:lang="en" resp="CH" modified="2019-12-25T07:04:00.796+09:00">                                    They replied:</seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2g0003_tls_006-20a.28" xml:lang="en" resp="CH" modified="2019-12-25T07:04:00.989+09:00">                                    "He is a man from Qí."</seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2g0003_tls_006-20a.29" xml:lang="en" resp="CH" modified="2019-12-25T07:04:13.385+09:00">The King said:</seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2g0003_tls_006-20a.30" xml:lang="en" resp="CH" modified="2019-12-25T07:04:16.472+09:00"/>
               <seg corresp="#KR2g0003_tls_006-20a.31" xml:lang="en" resp="CH" modified="2019-12-25T00:49:57.866+09:00">"What is he convicted of?"  "He is convicted of theft."</seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2g0003_tls_006-20a.32" xml:lang="en" resp="CH" modified="2019-12-25T00:50:41.068+09:00">The King looked at Master Yàn and said:</seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2g0003_tls_006-20a.33" xml:lang="en" resp="CH" modified="2019-12-25T00:51:16.694+09:00">"Are people from Qí congenitally prone to thievery?"</seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2g0003_tls_006-20a.34" xml:lang="en" resp="CH" modified="2019-12-25T00:51:42.446+09:00">Master Yàn left his mat and replied:</seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2g0003_tls_006-20a.35" xml:lang="en" resp="CH" modified="2019-12-25T00:52:03.795+09:00">"I have heard it said,</seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2g0003_tls_006-20a.36" xml:lang="en" resp="CH" modified="2019-12-25T00:53:44.468+09:00">if an orange that grows in Huáinán it produces sweet organges,</seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2g0003_tls_006-20a.37" xml:lang="en" resp="CH" modified="2019-12-25T00:54:38.88+09:00">but if it grows in Huáiběi it produces bitter oranges.</seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2g0003_tls_006-20a.38" xml:lang="en" resp="CH" modified="2019-12-25T00:55:17.159+09:00">The leaves are all similar</seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2g0003_tls_006-20a.39" xml:lang="en" resp="CH" modified="2019-12-25T00:55:30.923+09:00">but as for the fruits, their taste is different.</seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2g0003_tls_006-20a.40" xml:lang="en" resp="CH" modified="2019-12-25T00:55:43.376+09:00">Why is this?</seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2g0003_tls_006-20a.41" xml:lang="en" resp="CH" modified="2019-12-25T00:56:00.8+09:00">It is because the water and the earth in these places are different.</seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2g0003_tls_006-20a.42" xml:lang="en" resp="CH" modified="2019-12-25T00:56:48.608+09:00">Now if ordinary people are born and grow up in Qí they will not steal,</seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2g0003_tls_006-20a.43" xml:lang="en" resp="CH" modified="2019-12-25T00:57:16.209+09:00">but once they enter Chǔ they will steal.</seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2g0003_tls_006-20a.44" xml:lang="en" resp="CH" modified="2019-12-25T00:58:15.4+09:00">How could it ever e that this is not because the water and the earth of Chǔ causing these people to become prone to stealing."</seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2g0003_tls_006-20a.45" xml:lang="en" resp="CH" modified="2019-12-25T00:58:27.188+09:00">The King laughed and said:</seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2g0003_tls_006-20a.46" xml:lang="en" resp="CH" modified="2019-12-25T00:59:17.9+09:00">You, Sir, are not to be trifled with!</seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2g0003_tls_006-20a.21" xml:lang="en" resp="CH" modified="2019-12-25T01:11:13.829+09:00">Then Master Yàn arrived,</seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2g0003_tls_006-20a.22" xml:lang="en" resp="CH" modified="2019-12-25T01:11:58.034+09:00">the King of Chǔ presented Master Yàn with wine,</seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2g0003_tls_006-20a.23" xml:lang="en" resp="CH" modified="2019-12-25T01:12:13.287+09:00">and the wine was sweet enough.</seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2g0003_tls_006-20a.24" xml:lang="en" resp="CH" modified="2019-12-25T07:04:00.645+09:00">                                    Two magistrates put someone in fetters, came over to the king</seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2g0003_tls_006-20a.25" xml:lang="en" resp="CH" modified="2019-12-25T07:04:01.011+09:00">and then left. The King said:</seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2g0003_tls_006-20a.26" xml:lang="en" resp="CH" modified="2019-12-25T07:04:00.977+09:00">"The person in fetters, who is he?"</seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2g0003_tls_005-50a.1" xml:lang="en" resp="CH" modified="2019-12-25T07:10:56.66+09:00">When Master Yàn was serving as the Prime Minister of Qí</seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2g0003_tls_005-50a.2" xml:lang="en" resp="CH" modified="2019-12-25T07:11:28.005+09:00">and he went out for a trip</seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2g0003_tls_005-50a.3" xml:lang="en" resp="CH" modified="2019-12-25T07:21:32.544+09:00">his driver's wife from a crack in the door</seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2g0003_tls_005-50a.4" xml:lang="en" resp="CH" modified="2019-12-25T07:45:52.057+09:00">                                    observed her husband. Her husband, being the Prime Minister's driver,</seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2g0003_tls_005-50a.5" xml:lang="en" resp="CH" modified="2019-12-25T07:45:52.106+09:00">                                    was carrying a large parasol</seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2g0003_tls_005-50a.6" xml:lang="en" resp="CH" modified="2019-12-25T07:21:32.956+09:00">and he was whipping along his quartet of horses drawing his carriage.</seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2g0003_tls_005-50a.7" xml:lang="en" resp="CH" modified="2019-12-25T07:46:16.381+09:00">                                    His expression was proud and expansive:</seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2g0003_tls_005-50a.8" xml:lang="en" resp="CH" modified="2019-12-25T07:21:33+09:00">and he was very much pleased with himself.</seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2g0003_tls_005-50a.9" xml:lang="en" resp="CH" modified="2019-12-25T07:21:33.224+09:00">When, after a good while, he returned home</seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2g0003_tls_005-50a.10" xml:lang="en" resp="CH" modified="2019-12-25T07:46:52.998+09:00">                                    his wife asked to be divorced.</seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2g0003_tls_005-50a.11" xml:lang="en" resp="CH" modified="2019-12-25T07:21:33.646+09:00">The husband asked for the reason for this.</seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2g0003_tls_005-50a.12" xml:lang="en" resp="CH" modified="2019-12-25T07:21:33.883+09:00">The wife said:</seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2g0003_tls_005-50a.13" xml:lang="en" resp="CH" modified="2019-12-25T07:21:34.495+09:00">Master Yàn is not even a full eight chi tall,</seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2g0003_tls_005-50a.14" xml:lang="en" resp="CH" modified="2019-12-25T07:21:34.936+09:00">as a person he governs the state as a Prime Minister,</seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2g0003_tls_005-50a.15" xml:lang="en" resp="CH" modified="2019-12-25T07:21:35.939+09:00">and his fame is spread out to the feudal lords.</seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2g0003_tls_005-50a.16" xml:lang="en" resp="CH" modified="2019-12-25T07:22:11.496+09:00">But now as I see him set out on this trip</seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2g0003_tls_005-50a.17" xml:lang="en" resp="CH" modified="2019-12-25T07:22:44.063+09:00">his mind was deeply preoccupied.</seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2g0003_tls_005-50a.18" xml:lang="en" resp="CH" modified="2019-12-25T07:28:57.139+09:00">and all the time he found reason to respect others as being above him.</seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2g0003_tls_005-50a.19" xml:lang="en" resp="CH" modified="2019-12-25T07:29:18.837+09:00">Now you are eight chi tall</seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2g0003_tls_005-50a.21" xml:lang="en" resp="CH" modified="2019-12-25T07:31:22.388+09:00">And yet, as for your frame of mind</seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2g0003_tls_005-50a.22" xml:lang="en" resp="CH" modified="2019-12-25T07:31:43.344+09:00">you are all self-satisfied.</seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2g0003_tls_005-50a.23" xml:lang="en" resp="CH" modified="2019-12-25T07:32:03.775+09:00">So for this reason I am seeking to divorce you.</seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2g0003_tls_005-50a.24" xml:lang="en" resp="CH" modified="2019-12-25T07:32:55.155+09:00">Later on,</seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2g0003_tls_005-50a.25" xml:lang="en" resp="CH" modified="2019-12-25T07:34:06.168+09:00">the husband toned himself down</seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2g0003_tls_005-50a.26" xml:lang="en" resp="CH" modified="2019-12-25T07:34:38.463+09:00">and when Master Yàn, surprised asked him what was going on</seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2g0003_tls_005-50a.27" xml:lang="en" resp="CH" modified="2019-12-25T07:35:43.497+09:00">and the driver replied according to what had happened</seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2g0003_tls_005-50a.28" xml:lang="en" resp="CH" modified="2019-12-25T20:43:15.133+09:00">                                    Master Yàn recommended him and made him a grandee distinguished officer.</seg>
            <seg corresp="#KR2g0003_tls_001-1a.3-h" xml:lang="en" resp="#twharbsmeier" modified="2020-04-09T20:52:39.434+09:00"/>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2g0003_tls_001-1a.3" xml:lang="en" resp="#twharbsmeier" modified="2020-04-09T20:52:42.451+09:00">[Translation: Milburn] Lord Zhuang estemed the Brave and Physically Strong, and Did Not Pay  Any Attention to Proper Bevaviour. Master Yan Remonstrated</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2g0003_tls_001-2a.1" xml:lang="en" resp="#twharbsmeier" modified="2020-04-09T20:53:07.44+09:00">Lord Zhuang was only impressed by bravery and physical strength,</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2g0003_tls_001-2a.2" xml:lang="en" resp="#twharbsmeier" modified="2020-04-09T20:53:54.393+09:00">and paid no attention to proper behaviour.</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2g0003_tls_001-2a.3" xml:lang="en" resp="#twharbsmeier" modified="2020-04-09T21:02:12.522+09:00">Knights who were brave and strong</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2g0003_tls_001-2a.4" xml:lang="en" resp="#twharbsmeier" modified="2020-04-09T21:08:44.897+09:00">were under no constraints within the state [of Qi],</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2g0003_tls_001-2a.5" xml:lang="en" resp="#twharbsmeier" modified="2020-04-09T21:09:20.62+09:00">members of the nobility and relatives of the lord did not make loyal representations,</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2g0003_tls_001-2a.6" xml:lang="en" resp="#twharbsmeier" modified="2020-04-09T21:13:10.62+09:00">and his closest advisors did not point out his mistakes.</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2g0003_tls_001-2a.7" xml:lang="en" resp="#twharbsmeier" modified="2020-04-09T22:01:12.813+09:00">Therefore Master Yan had audience with his lord.</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2g0003_tls_001-2a.8" xml:lang="en" resp="#twharbsmeier" modified="2020-04-09T22:03:54.089+09:00">The lord said:</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2g0003_tls_001-2a.9" xml:lang="en" resp="#twharbsmeier" modified="2020-04-09T22:04:49.806+09:00">In the past, were there also other men whose positions in the world were established thanks to their followers' bravery and physical strength?"</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2g0003_tls_001-2a.10" xml:lang="en" resp="#twharbsmeier" modified="2020-04-09T22:18:11.162+09:00">Master Yan replied:</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2g0003_tls_001-2a.11" xml:lang="en" resp="#twharbsmeier" modified="2020-04-09T22:18:55.311+09:00">I have heard it said </seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2g0003_tls_001-2a.12" xml:lang="en" resp="#twharbsmeier" modified="2020-04-09T22:19:18.236+09:00">that to disregard death in order to put the principles of ritual propriety into action  is what is called "bravery;"</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2g0003_tls_001-2a.13" xml:lang="en" resp="#twharbsmeier" modified="2020-04-09T22:19:57.982+09:00">executing violent men and not running away from the powerful is what is called "strength."</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2g0003_tls_001-2a.14" xml:lang="en" resp="#twharbsmeier" modified="2020-04-09T22:33:21.343+09:00">But those whose positions have been established thanks to bravery and physical strength</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2g0003_tls_001-2a.15" xml:lang="en" resp="#twharbsmeier" modified="2020-04-09T22:33:33.227+09:00">must then put into practice ritual propriety and justice.</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2g0003_tls_001-2a.17" xml:lang="en" resp="#twharbsmeier" modified="2020-04-10T03:07:01.954+09:00">they united many countries and yet they were not greedy;</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2g0003_tls_001-2a.18" xml:lang="en" resp="#twharbsmeier" modified="2020-04-10T03:09:08.361+09:00">this is the principle of kindness and justice.</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2g0003_tls_001-2a.19" xml:lang="en" resp="#twharbsmeier" modified="2020-04-10T03:11:23.74+09:00">To execute a violent criminal and not to run away from the powerful;</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2g0003_tls_001-2a.20" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2020-04-13T01:23:42.768+09:00">to right wrongs without caring how many people are involved: [deal with/remove criminals? CH]</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2g0003_tls_001-2a.21" xml:lang="en" resp="#twharbsmeier" modified="2020-04-10T03:21:04.507+09:00">such are the deeds of brave and strong men.</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2g0003_tls_001-2a.22" xml:lang="en" resp="#twharbsmeier" modified="2020-04-10T03:21:19.072+09:00">The brave and strong men of antiquity</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2g0003_tls_001-2a.23" xml:lang="en" resp="#twharbsmeier" modified="2020-04-10T03:21:29.781+09:00">put ritual propriety and justice into action,</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2g0003_tls_001-2a.24" xml:lang="en" resp="#twharbsmeier" modified="2020-04-10T03:26:12.946+09:00">but now rulers lack the principles of kindness and justice,</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2g0003_tls_001-2a.25" xml:lang="en" resp="#twharbsmeier" modified="2020-04-10T03:26:39.793+09:00">and their subjects do not right wrongs or punish violent criminals</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2g0003_tls_001-2a.26" xml:lang="en" resp="#twharbsmeier" modified="2020-04-10T03:34:55.198+09:00">People owe their position in the world to nothing more than bravery and physical strength.</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2g0003_tls_001-2a.27" xml:lang="en" resp="#twharbsmeier" modified="2020-04-10T03:35:25.216+09:00">But when the feudal lords do this, then the country is endangered;</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2g0003_tls_001-2a.28" xml:lang="en" resp="#twharbsmeier" modified="2020-04-10T03:35:59.453+09:00">when ordinary people behave in this way then their families are ruined.</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2g0003_tls_001-2a.29" xml:lang="en" resp="#twharbsmeier" modified="2020-04-11T22:46:43.223+09:00">In the past when the Xia dynasty declined,</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2g0003_tls_001-2a.30" xml:lang="en" resp="#twharbsmeier" modified="2020-04-11T22:56:15.625+09:00">there was Tui Yi and Da Xi,</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2g0003_tls_001-2a.32" xml:lang="en" resp="#twharbsmeier" modified="2020-04-11T22:55:37.393+09:00">there was Fei Zhong and Wu Lai.</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2g0003_tls_001-2a.33" xml:lang="en" resp="#twharbsmeier" modified="2020-04-11T22:58:54.11+09:00">Their feet could walk one thousand li,</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2g0003_tls_001-2a.34" xml:lang="en" resp="#twharbsmeier" modified="2020-04-11T22:58:55.898+09:00"> their hands could rip apart a tiger or a rhinoceros,</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2g0003_tls_001-2a.35" xml:lang="en" resp="#twharbsmeier" modified="2020-04-11T23:04:30.681+09:00">and they were employed thanks to their physical strength,</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2g0003_tls_001-2a.36" xml:lang="en" resp="#twharbsmeier" modified="2020-04-11T23:04:52.543+09:00">but they bullied and killed the [people of the] world;</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2g0003_tls_001-2a.37" xml:lang="en" resp="#twharbsmeier" modified="2020-04-11T23:10:16.157+09:00">they terrorized and executed the innocent,</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2g0003_tls_001-2a.38" xml:lang="en" resp="#twharbsmeier" modified="2020-04-11T23:14:17.608+09:00">praising bravery and physical strength</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2g0003_tls_001-2a.39" xml:lang="en" resp="#twharbsmeier" modified="2020-04-11T23:14:30.731+09:00">and paying no attention to the principles of justice.</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2g0003_tls_001-2a.40" xml:lang="en" resp="#twharbsmeier" modified="2020-04-11T23:21:25.846+09:00">This is the reason why [King] Jie [of the Xia dynasty] and [King] Zhou [of the Shang dynasty] </seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2g0003_tls_001-2a.41" xml:lang="en" resp="#twharbsmeier" modified="2020-04-11T23:25:49.809+09:00">and the Xia and Shang dynasties fell.</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2g0003_tls_001-2a.42" xml:lang="en" resp="#twharbsmeier" modified="2020-04-11T23:26:08.927+09:00">Now your lordship is impressed by bravery and physical strength,</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2g0003_tls_001-2a.43" xml:lang="en" resp="#twharbsmeier" modified="2020-04-11T23:26:17.493+09:00">and pays no attention to proper behaviour.</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2g0003_tls_001-2a.44" xml:lang="en" resp="#twharbsmeier" modified="2020-04-11T23:36:04.137+09:00">Knights who are brave and strong</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2g0003_tls_001-2a.45" xml:lang="en" resp="#twharbsmeier" modified="2020-04-11T23:36:25.023+09:00">are under no constraints within the state [of Qi],</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2g0003_tls_001-2a.46" xml:lang="en" resp="#twharbsmeier" modified="2020-04-11T23:36:55.012+09:00">where they can establish their status by intimidation and brute force</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2g0003_tls_001-2a.47" xml:lang="en" resp="#twharbsmeier" modified="2020-04-11T23:37:07.637+09:00">even though their actions are wicked and criminal.</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2g0003_tls_001-2a.48" xml:lang="en" resp="#twharbsmeier" modified="2020-04-11T23:37:33.232+09:00">Members of the nobility and relatives of the lord do not make loyal representations,</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2g0003_tls_001-2a.49" xml:lang="en" resp="#twharbsmeier" modified="2020-04-11T23:37:47.873+09:00">and your closest advisors do not point out your mistakes.</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2g0003_tls_001-2a.50" xml:lang="en" resp="#twharbsmeier" modified="2020-04-11T23:38:08.254+09:00">This is contrary to the virtuos principles of the Sage-Kings,</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2g0003_tls_001-2a.51" xml:lang="en" resp="#twharbsmeier" modified="2020-04-11T23:38:20.434+09:00">but is what you would expect from a doomed ruler.</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2g0003_tls_001-2a.52" xml:lang="en" resp="#twharbsmeier" modified="2020-04-11T23:38:47.26+09:00">I have never heard of a [a ruler] who behaved in this way and survived."</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2g0003_tls_001-3a.2" xml:lang="en" resp="#twharbsmeier" modified="2020-04-12T18:03:16.588+09:00">Lord Jing was Drinking Wine, and Became Drunk. He Wanted His Grandees Not to Consider the Demands of Ritual Propriety. Master Yan Remonstrated</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2g0003_tls_001-4a.2" xml:lang="en" resp="#twharbsmeier" modified="2020-04-12T18:06:48.049+09:00">and he said:</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2g0003_tls_001-4a.3" xml:lang="en" resp="#twharbsmeier" modified="2020-04-12T18:09:52.275+09:00">Today I want to enjoy drinking with my grandees;</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2g0003_tls_001-4a.4" xml:lang="en" resp="#twharbsmeier" modified="2020-04-12T18:09:58.725+09:00">therefore you have my permission to act without considering ritual propriety."</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2g0003_tls_001-4a.5" xml:lang="en" resp="#twharbsmeier" modified="2020-04-12T18:19:48.718+09:00">Master Yan's expression changed to one of distress and he said:</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2g0003_tls_001-4a.6" xml:lang="en" resp="#twharbsmeier" modified="2020-04-12T18:22:21.861+09:00">"Your lordship i s wrong in what you say!</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2g0003_tls_001-4a.7" xml:lang="en" resp="#twharbsmeier" modified="2020-04-12T18:22:56.558+09:00">Your subjects would definitely want your lordship to agree to set aside demands of ritual propriety.</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2g0003_tls_001-4a.8" xml:lang="en" resp="#twharbsmeier" modified="2020-04-12T18:28:30.807+09:00">There are those who are strong enough to overpower their rulers,</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2g0003_tls_001-4a.9" xml:lang="en" resp="#twharbsmeier" modified="2020-04-12T18:28:41.747+09:00">there are those who are daring enough to assasinate their rulers,</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2g0003_tls_001-4a.10" xml:lang="en" resp="#twharbsmeier" modified="2020-04-12T18:28:51.992+09:00">but they are held back by ritual propriety.</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2g0003_tls_001-4a.11" xml:lang="en" resp="#twharbsmeier" modified="2020-04-12T18:39:58.344+09:00">The birds and the beasts are governed by brute force,</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2g0003_tls_001-4a.12" xml:lang="en" resp="#twharbsmeier" modified="2020-04-12T18:40:06.707+09:00">whereby the strong oppress the weak,</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2g0003_tls_001-4a.13" xml:lang="en" resp="#twharbsmeier" modified="2020-04-12T18:40:18.092+09:00">and therefore they constantly change their leaders.</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2g0003_tls_001-4a.14" xml:lang="en" resp="#twharbsmeier" modified="2020-04-12T18:40:44.494+09:00">Now if your lordship were to disregard the claims of ritual propriety,</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2g0003_tls_001-4a.15" xml:lang="en" resp="#twharbsmeier" modified="2020-04-12T18:40:59.255+09:00">you would be reducing yourself to the level of the birds and beasts.</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2g0003_tls_001-4a.16" xml:lang="en" resp="#twharbsmeier" modified="2020-04-12T18:41:20.852+09:00">If your subjects are to be governed by brute force,</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2g0003_tls_001-4a.18" xml:lang="en" resp="#twharbsmeier" modified="2020-04-12T18:43:01.924+09:00">and the leader is constantly changed,</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2g0003_tls_001-4a.19" xml:lang="en" resp="#twharbsmeier" modified="2020-04-12T18:43:26.512+09:00">will your lordship's position be safe?</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2g0003_tls_001-2a.16" xml:lang="en" resp="#twharbsmeier" modified="2020-04-13T01:25:03.44+09:00">[King] Tang [of the Shang dynasty] and [King] Wu [of the Zhou dynasty] made  use of their military might and yet they were not rebels;</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2g0003_tls_006-32a.15" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2020-04-28T23:16:04.21+09:00">That is the reason for which I did not presume to accept it.</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2g0003_tls_007-40a.12" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2020-05-07T01:42:13.039+09:00">then I beg to commit suicide for that.</seg>
                </p>
         </div>
